code: @Override public void setBeanFactory(BeanFactory beanFactory) {     this.beanFactory = beanFactory. }

@Override public MessageChannel resolveDestination(String name) {     Assert.state(this.beanFactory != null, "No BeanFactory configured").     try {         return this.beanFactory.getBean(name, MessageChannel.class).     } catch (BeansException ex) {         throw new DestinationResolutionException("Failed to find MessageChannel bean with name '" + name + "'", ex).     } }
